plot: Nozomu is fed up of people going on about his name at a salary office. He later takes certificate examinations and passes them all - except for one that tests his ability to commit suicide.
title: "Zoku sayonara zetsubô sensei" Hyakumankai Iwareta Neko/Akazukin-chan, neru. Ki o Tsukete/Tsugaru Tsushin Kyoiku
